{"tid":953392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲仔去完廁所跌倒 昏迷送院不治","createTime":"2018-12-24T02:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T03:48:23.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb9a16d1ec36def11b5a47932147c5d666bf935","tid":953392,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:05:53.000Z","msg":"凌晨5時許，牛頭角下邨貴輝樓一單位，一名18歲姓陳男子，據知起床去洗手間後返回床邊時跌倒昏迷，家人發現報警，他被送院搶救，惜終告不治，趕到醫院了解的家人得知噩耗後痛哭，警員到場調查，初步沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59064245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59064245&d=JcB2XAMnINmnq8cHyxjvOtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d761c592\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59064245&h=982b9330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59064245</a>"},{"pid":"4f4fb6ea455bf752c540db77e918d1004f13ed1f","tid":953392,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3f1c78ee92bd7125a2511642ad5ae496c3b842b","tid":953392,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，新下邨都已經唔係畀香港人住。"},{"pid":"89922dc5bde9f26b28801858bf3ff89b5ff3a548","tid":953392,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a1448fe008c1c60263efbbef69496bd94cbd5e","tid":953392,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3f1c78ee92bd7125a2511642ad5ae496c3b842b","tid":953392,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，新下邨都已經唔係畀香港人住。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:42:34.000Z","msg":"都仲有本地 , 唔多"},{"pid"